  MODULE .......: PBANKREP
  FUNCTION .....: List payments' bank accounts
  APPLICATION ..: TMS
  AUTHOR .......: aam
  CREATED ......: 08.11.02
  MODIFIED .....: 12.09.03/aam brand
                  21.04.05/aam skip payment type 6  
  VERSION ......: M15
